column5: Boat show slow tonght.  Sales way down from last year.  The Lund guy said his prices are up 4% plus exchange of 10%  Saw something cool.  ATV/Jetski combo.  http://www.gibbssports.com/quadski
That would be a great toy to have and just think, you'd be able to piss off the fishers in the boats and the people on the beach. LOL  Dan.
My impression was that Cdn boat prices were higher than their US counterparts anyway.    If so, funny that the difference in exchange rate has a direct proportional impact on pricing upwards.
